item.title: Crackmes.de - The_thing by prout
item.description: This is a crackme level 2 (Easy) from https://crackmes.one/crackme/5ab77f5433c5d40ad448c1d6 ) Fast static analysis First, let’s see what kind of file is it with file command : $ file thething thething: ELF 32-bit LSB executable, Intel 80386, version 1 (SYSV), for GNU/Linux 2.4.1, dynamically linked, interpreter /lib/ld-linux.so.2, no section header Ok, so 32 bits ELF and dynamically linked (this detail will be useful later). Not sure if stripped or not because of the “no section header”.
